Different models may vary, but make sure you pour enough water into the tank of the machine so that the pump pipes are fully submerged. Turn on the power and the pump to pump water into the boiler. Turn on the boiler to heat the water. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/d/dc/Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/v4-459px-Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/d/dc/Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet1.jpg/aid135288-v4-728px-Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"485","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

The handle that holds the coffee is called the group handle and this should be locked into the machine. The light on the machine will go out when the water is at the correct temperature. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/0/03/Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/v4-459px-Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/0/03/Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet2.jpg/aid135288-v4-728px-Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"485","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Turn off the boiler and press the dosage button to let water flow through the handle for about 10 seconds. This will clean it through and heat it to the same temperature as the water. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/b/b5/Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/v4-459px-Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","bigUrl":"/images/thumb/b/b5/Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet3.jpg/aid135288-v4-728px-Make-Flavoured-Coffee-Step-1Bullet3.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":"728","bigHeight":"485","licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
